Class User

java.lang.Object
team5.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
CareerCenterStaff, CompanyRep, Student
public class User extends Object
Represents a base user in the internship placement management system. This class serves as the parent class for all user types including Student, CompanyRep, and CareerCenterStaff. It provides common user attributes and functionalities such as login, logout, and password management.

    • changePassword

      public boolean changePassword()
      Allows the user to change their password through a three-stage verification process. The process includes verifying the old password, entering a new password (which must differ from the old one), and confirming the new password. Each stage allows up to two attempts before returning to the main menu.
      Returns:
      true if the password change is successful, false if the user exits or exceeds the maximum number of attempts at any stage
